<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Many thanks for taking on the role of {!Job_placement__c.Role__c} on the NCS: Real Challenge Action (RCA) and (if applicable) NCS: Graduations days. &nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The total gross pay for your work on {!Job_placement__c.Assignment_end_date__c} will be&nbsp;</font><font><font face="arial">{!Job_placement__c.Total_gross_pay__c}&nbsp;for&nbsp;</font></font></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This will be subject to tax and NI deductions.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">You will receive your pay for this on 16 December 2014.&nbsp;</span></div></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">On your payslip&nbsp;</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">(sent via email on&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c})</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">, you will see the total amount which you will receive.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial" size="2">Due to new auto-</font><font size="2">enrolment</font><font face="arial" size="2">&nbsp;legislation, employees of The Challenge, including seasonal staff, may be enrolled in a workplace pension scheme. This is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer.&nbsp;</font></font><font face="arial" size="2">For further information, please go to&nbsp;</font><a href="http://www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">www.gov.uk/workplace-<wbr>pensions</a><font face="arial" size="2">.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial" size="2">&nbsp;</font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">Further information about workplace pensions and how to opt-out can be found on the staffing website under FAQs.&nbsp;</span></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.3333330154419px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><br></span></div><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">If you have any questions, please contact your staffing associate. Please quote the email reference number in any correspondence.</span></p></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Yours sincerely,</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">NCS with The Challenge</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0